location.fullValue: No 1 Condo Of Paradise Harbour  Of North Palm Beac

data.description: Enjoy gracious tropical living in this beautifully maintained, split bedroom, 2bd/2ba gem in Lake Harbour Towers. The perfect view awaits! This gorgeous south-east exposure is guaranteed to delight; sparkling blue intracoastal waters, lush green lawn, and views of the city in the distance. Amenities include two rooftop swimming pools, outdoor seating and grills and as well as a  lively social room. Residents enjoy on-site billiard table, shuffleboard, and putting green. Stroll along the waterfront or head over to historic Kelsey Park for a game of pickleball or tennis. Close to the action, yet peaceful and serene. 10 minutes to the Gardens Mall, the beach, and PGA Blvd. with its restaurants and shopping. 20 minutes to the PBI
